<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Prestige Group</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/prestige.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="prestige-header-new">
        <!-- Black Top Bar -->
        <div class="prestige-top-bar" style="background: #000; padding: 15px 0; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1001; height: 70px; display: flex; align-items: center;">
            <div class="prestige-container" style="width: 100%;">
                <div class="prestige-top-content" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 100%;">
                    <nav class="prestige-nav">
                        <ul class="prestige-nav-menu" style="display: flex; list-style: none; justify-content: space-between; width: 100%; max-width: 800px; margin: 0; padding: 0 40px; align-items: center;">
                            <li><a href="/" class="prestige-nav-link" style="color: white; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease; position: relative; line-height: 1;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#d4af37'" onmouseout="this.style.color='white'">Home</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/all-projects" class="prestige-nav-link" style="color: white; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease; position: relative; line-height: 1;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#d4af37'" onmouseout="this.style.color='white'">All Projects</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/about-us" class="prestige-nav-link active-nav" style="color: #d4af37; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease; position: relative; line-height: 1;">About Us</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/blog" class="prestige-nav-link" style="color: white; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease; position: relative; line-height: 1;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#d4af37'" onmouseout="this.style.color='white'">Blog</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/contact" class="prestige-nav-link" style="color: white; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease; position: relative; line-height: 1;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#d4af37'" onmouseout="this.style.color='white'">Contact</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Logo positioned between black and transparent sections -->
        <div class="prestige-logo-bridge" style="position: fixed; top: 50px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); z-index: 1002; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); padding: 10px 25px; border-radius: 25px; border: 2px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.3);">
            <div class="prestige-logo">
                <h2 style="color: #d4af37; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; margin: 0; font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1; text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">PRESTIGE</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Transparent Decorative Bar -->
        <div class="prestige-transparent-bar" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); padding: 8px 0; position: fixed; top: 70px; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
            <div class="prestige-container" style="width: 100%; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;">
                <div class="prestige-decorative-content" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-weight: 300;">
                    <span>Premium Real Estate Solutions</span>
                    <span>•</span>
                    <span>Luxury Living Redefined</span>
                    <span>•</span>
                    <span>Excellence in Construction</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="prestige-hero">
        <div class="prestige-hero-bg"></div>
        <div class="prestige-hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="prestige-hero-content">
            <h1 class="prestige-hero-title">About Prestige Group</h1>
            <p class="prestige-hero-subtitle">Three decades of excellence in crafting India's most prestigious developments</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Prestige Construction is synonymous with excellence in the real estate market. With over three decades of experience, we have been transforming the landscape of India's major cities with landmark developments.</p>
            <p>We take immense pride in crafting residential projects that redefine luxury living. From stylish apartments in gated communities to opulent villas, each Prestige development is a testament to architectural brilliance and uncompromising quality.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Legacy & Vision -->
    <section class="woody-section prestige-woody-pad">
        <div class="prestige-container">
            <div class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
                <h2 style="color:#fff">Legacy & Vision</h2>
                <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">From our first boutique project in Bengaluru to pan-India developments, our journey has been about elevating everyday life.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px,1fr)); gap: 24px;">
                <div class="woody-card" style="padding:22px; border-radius:16px;">
                    <h3 class="prestige-card-title" style="color:#fff; margin-bottom:8px;">Design First</h3>
                    <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9)">Architect-led planning, climate-responsive facades, and timeless interiors that age beautifully.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="woody-card" style="padding:22px; border-radius:16px;">
                    <h3 class="prestige-card-title" style="color:#fff; margin-bottom:8px;">Engineering Excellence</h3>
                    <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9)">IS codes compliance, seismic-ready structures, and material selection driven by performance.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="woody-card" style="padding:22px; border-radius:16px;">
                    <h3 class="prestige-card-title" style="color:#fff; margin-bottom:8px;">People & Places</h3>
                    <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9)">Communities that foster belonging with curated amenities, greener landscapes and safer streets.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="woody-card" style="padding:22px; border-radius:16px;">
                    <h3 class="prestige-card-title" style="color:#fff; margin-bottom:8px;">Aftercare</h3>
                    <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9)">Dedicated handover teams, digital support, and facility management to ensure worry‑free living.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Milestones -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px,1fr)); gap:24px; text-align:center;">
            <div class="prestige-card" style="padding:28px; border-radius:16px;">
                <h3 style="color:var(--prestige-secondary); font-size:2.2rem;">35+</h3>
                <p>Years Building</p>
            </div>
            <div class="prestige-card" style="padding:28px; border-radius:16px;">
                <h3 style="color:var(--prestige-secondary); font-size:2.2rem;">8</h3>
                <p>Major Cities</p>
            </div>
            <div class="prestige-card" style="padding:28px; border-radius:16px;">
                <h3 style="color:var(--prestige-secondary); font-size:2.2rem;">300+</h3>
                <p>Completed Projects</p>
            </div>
            <div class="prestige-card" style="padding:28px; border-radius:16px;">
                <h3 style="color:var(--prestige-secondary); font-size:2.2rem;">50+</h3>
                <p>Ongoing Developments</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
      // Keep nav visible and premium while scrolling
      window.addEventListener('scroll', function(){
        const header = document.querySelector('.prestige-header-new');
        if(!header) return;
        if(window.scrollY > 50){ header.classList.add('scrolled'); }
        else { header.classList.remove('scrolled'); }
      });
    </script>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <div class="footer-logo">PRESTIGE</div>
                    <p class="footer-description">India's leading real estate developer, crafting premium residential and commercial spaces across major cities for over three decades.</p>
                    <div class="footer-social">
                        <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4 class="footer-title">Quick Links</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/all-projects">All Projects</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4 class="footer-title">Services</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="#">Residential Projects</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Commercial Spaces</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Villa Communities</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Luxury Apartments</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Investment Opportunities</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4 class="footer-title">Contact Info</h4>
                    <div class="footer-contact">
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                            <span>Prestige House, Brigade Road<br>Bangalore, Karnataka 560001</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                            <span>+91 80 2559 1234</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                            <span>info@prestigegroup.info</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <div class="footer-bottom-content">
                    <p>&copy; 2024 Prestige Group. All rights reserved.</p>
                    <div class="footer-bottom-links">
                        <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
                        <a href="#">Terms of Service</a>
                        <a href="#">Cookie Policy</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
    
    <style>
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .prestige-logo-bridge {
                top: 45px !important;
                padding: 8px 20px !important;
            }
            
            .prestige-logo-bridge h2 {
                font-size: 1.4rem !important;
            }
            
            .prestige-nav-menu {
                max-width: 600px !important;
                padding: 0 20px !important;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .prestige-logo-bridge {
                top: 42px !important;
                padding: 6px 15px !important;
            }
            
            .prestige-logo-bridge h2 {
                font-size: 1.2rem !important;
            }
            
            .prestige-nav-menu {
                max-width: 100% !important;
                padding: 0 10px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
    
    <script>
        // Header scroll behavior
        window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {
            const header = document.querySelector('.prestige-header-new');
            if (header) {
                if (window.scrollY > 100) {
                    header.classList.add('scrolled');
                } else {
                    header.classList.remove('scrolled');
                }
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>